content:
You can now choose an additional data space for Segment Intelligence, offering greater flexibility for segmenting your data. Previously, you could only use the default data space.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer editions with a Data Cloud Starter license.

When: This change is available starting in July 2024.

How: To set up Segment Intelligence for a data space, go to Setup and search for Segintel.
title: Salesforce Summer '24 Release Notes
